    "Reporting and critical appraisal of research findings: in the final step, the collected findings are integrated into the framework and condensed for clarity.",
    "Information Table 1 Keywords used in the database search Group A: search strings related to CEXs or DEXs Group B: search strings related to cryptocurrency markets \"AMM\" \"Bitcoin\" \"Automated Market Maker/ing\" \"Blockchain/s\" \"Bitcoin Exchange/s\" \"Coin/s\" \"CEX/s\" \"Cryptocurrency/ies\" \"Centralized\"",
